'''Squad Four''' was a squad of [[Alpha-3 Nimbus-class V-wing starfighter/Legends|Alpha-3 ''Nimbus''-class V-wing starfighters]] tasked with protecting [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]. The squad's fighters were painted gray with maroon markings, including a vertical jagged stripe visible when the wings were in flight position.

==History==
When [[Supreme Chancellor/Legends|Supreme Chancellor]] [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]] was kidnapped in [[19 BBY/Legends|19 BBY]], Squad Four and [[Clone Flight Squad Seven/Legends|Clone Fight Squad Seven]] attacked the [[Invisible Hand/Legends|''Invisible Hand'']] in an attempt to help [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Anakin Skywalker]] and [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]] rescue him.

